<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none; padding:0;">
<div class="NavHead" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #C00; background: none; text-align: left;">History</div>
<div class="NavContent" style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align:center;"><a href="/wiki/Anarchism_and_Marxism" title="Anarchism and Marxism">Anarchism and Marxism</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Capitalist_mode_of_production" title="Capitalist mode of production">Capitalist production</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Class_struggle" title="Class struggle">Class struggle</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Dictatorship_of_the_proletariat" title="Dictatorship of the proletariat">Dictatorship of the proletariat</a><br />
