<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Friedrich_Engels" title="Friedrich Engels">Friedrich Engels</a> advances such a conceptual model in his Appendix to <a href="/wiki/Karl_Marx" title="Karl Marx">Marx'</a> <a href="http://www.marxists.org/archive/marx/works/1894-c3/supp.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.marxists.org/archive/marx/works/1894-c3/supp.htm" rel="nofollow">Capital v. III</a></li>
